    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil forces swarm and threaten to destroy all of time. A tiny jumping spider must swing into action to save the past, present and future from multiversal invasion!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Swing Through Levels!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use webs to swing around at breakneck speed! Dodge armoured enemies and expose their weakpoints to attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/dcd98f61ead5402b0301a3ea99770595.poster.avif?t=1770892287\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/dcd98f61ead5402b0301a3ea99770595.webm?t=1770892287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/dcd98f61ead5402b0301a3ea99770595.mp4?t=1770892287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shoot Webs!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >String together enemies for combo attacks. You can even manipulate the environment, flinging objects and turning hazards into deadly traps. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/a348d4ff5c24cb514b14256481b90b26.poster.avif?t=1770892287\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/a348d4ff5c24cb514b14256481b90b26.webm?t=1770892287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/a348d4ff5c24cb514b14256481b90b26.mp4?t=1770892287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build a Thread of Items!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect items from different time periods which synergize depending on their position and connections. Many items grant others stack bonuses which can be chained for massive power. Your foes scale exponentially, so you must rely on increasingly absurd combos to survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/74296f319b316c99a794f60b801736f6.poster.avif?t=1770892287\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/74296f319b316c99a794f60b801736f6.webm?t=1770892287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018720/extras/74296f319b316c99a794f60b801736f6.mp4?t=1770892287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle Through Time!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Time Rogues and save the past, present and future from total destruction...</p>",
